ass=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">19</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"date\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Date Released</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">March 19th, 2016</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"issue\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">WSJ Issue</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">16, 2016</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"arc\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Arc</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Final_Selection_Arc\" title=\"Final Selection Arc\">Final Selection Arc</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"anime episode\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Anime Episode(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Episode_4\" title=\"Episode 4\">Episode 4</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Guide</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"previous\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_5\" title=\"Chapter 5\">Chapter 5</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"next\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_7\" title=\"Chapter 7\">Chapter 7</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n<nav class=\"pi-navigation pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background pi-secondary-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Chapter_6_Images\" title=\"Category:Chapter 6 Images\">Chapter 6 Images</a></nav>\n</aside>\n\n<b>A Mountain of Hands</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\"><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">山</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>やま</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby>ほどの<ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">手</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>て</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby>が</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Yamahodo no tega</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Installing Japanese character sets\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#198975;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is the sixth chapter of <a href=\"/wiki/Koyoharu_Got%C5%8Dge\" title=\"Koyoharu Gotōge\">Koyoharu Gotōge's</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" title=\"Kimetsu no Yaiba (Manga)\">Kimetsu no Yaiba</a>.\n<p></p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summary\">Summary</span></h2>\n<p>The chapter starts off with <a href=\"/wiki/Sakonji_Urokodaki\" title=\"Sakonji Urokodaki\">Sakonji Urokodaki</a> giving a bit of background information about defeating demons. He points out that Demon's must be decapitated at the neck and that it can only be done with a special blade called a <a href=\"/wiki/Nichirin_Blade\" title=\"Nichirin Blade\">Nichirin Swords</a>.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/0/0d/Sakonji_commends_Tanjiro_for_finishing_his_training.png/revision/latest?cb=20200930161432\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Sakonji_commends_Tanjiro_for_finishing_his_training.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"90\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Sakonji_commends_Tanjiro_for_finishing_his_training.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Sakonji giving Tanjiro his blessing.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>The scene flashes to <a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro</a> completing his training for the <a href=\"/wiki/Final_Selection_Arc\" title=\"Final Selection Arc\">Final Selection</a>, and realizing his newly acquired technique of smelling the 'lines of intervals'. He meets with <a href=\"/wiki/Sakonji_Urokodaki\" title=\"Sakonji Urokodaki\">Urokodaki</a> who praises his abilities and hard work before giving him his blessing to participate in the selection. He pleads with Tanjiro&nbsp;to survive and return back to him and <a href=\"/wiki/Nezuko_Kamado\" title=\"Nezuko Kamado\">Nezuko</a> alive.\n</p><p>Before setting off, Tanjiro&nbsp;receives a hand carved fox mask, similar to the ones worn by <a href=\"/wiki/Sabito\" title=\"Sabito\">Sabito</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Makomo\" title=\"Makomo\">Makomo</a>, from Urokodaki and says goodbye to a sleeping Nezuko. He bids Urokodaki farewell, entrusting him to care for Nezuko, Sabito, and Makomo while he's away, Urokodaki is left astonished as he reveals that Sabito and Makomo were the deceased spirits of his previous students and that Tanjiro&nbsp;shouldn't have known who they were.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c6/Final_Selection.png/revision/latest?cb=20180830064317\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Final_Selection.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"160\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Final_Selection.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Arrival at the Final Selection</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Having just arrived to the Final Selection at Mount Fujikasane, Tanjiro&nbsp;admires the wisteria flowers glistening the steps as he climbs the stairs. Once he reaches the top, he encounters a large number of swordsmen waiting to participate in the event. Two curators organizing the event, inform the students that the Wisteria flowers seen along the path, serves as demon repellent on the mountain. They go further on to explain that in order to pass the selection, they must survive for seven nights in the region of the mountain where the Wisteria doesn't bloom, and where the demons roam free.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tright show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 152px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/8/8d/Demons.png/revision/latest?cb=20160603225300\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Demons.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"154\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Demons.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Demons fighting over rights to kill Tanjiro</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Once the selection begins, Tanjiro&nbsp;immediately encounters two demons who bicker over the rights to kill and eat Tanjiro. He utilizes the <b>Water Breathing: Fourth Form - Striking Tide</b> to slice the 'threads' that he smelled, and successfully defeats the demons which boosts his confidence in completing the selection.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 152px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/e/e4/Hand_Demon_body.png/revision/latest?cb=20161009064054\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Hand_Demon_body.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"219\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/e/e4/Hand_Demon_body.png/revision/latest?cb=20161009064054\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/e/e4/Hand_Demon_body.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20161009064054\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"219\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Hand Demon body.png\" data-image-key=\"Hand_Demon_body.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/e/e4/Hand_Demon_body.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20161009064054\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Hand_Demon_body.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">The deformed demon that Tanjiro encounters</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure><p>As he takes a moment to pray for the demon's souls, he is caught off guard by a powerful overwhelming smell, and the screams of a swordsman running away. When he turns to face the sound, he is witnesses a large <a href=\"/wiki/Hand_Demon\" title=\"Hand Demon\">deformed demon</a>&nbsp;chasing the swordsman while carrying a deceased boy by the throat. As the boy runs, the demon suddenly manifests a gigantic arm that grabs the boy by the leg pulling him into the air. Tanjiro stands in fear but wills himself to use his skill to help save the boy. Before the demon is able to eat the boy, Tanjiro&nbsp;intervenes by using <b>Water Breathing: Second Form - Water Wheel</b> to slice one of the limbs off of the demon, who glaring back at Tanjiro commenting that \"Another of [his] dear foxes has come!\"\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Sakonji_Urokodaki\" title=\"Sakonji Urokodaki\">Sakonji Urokodaki</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sabito\" title=\"Sabito\">Sabito</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nezuko_Kamado\" title=\"Nezuko Kamado\">Nezuko Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Makomo\" title=\"Makomo\">Makomo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Genya_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Genya Shinazugawa\">Genya Shinazugawa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Zenitsu_Agatsuma\" title=\"Zenitsu Agatsuma\">Zenitsu Agatsuma</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kanao_Tsuyuri\" title=\"Kanao Tsuyuri\">Kanao Tsuyuri</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hand_Demon\" title=\"Hand Demon\">Hand Demon</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Tanjiro&nbsp;learns how to master the Breathing techniques</li>\n<li>Tanjiro&nbsp;enters and participates in the Final Selection</li></ul>\n\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20210109210557\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.197 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.222 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 9290/1000000\nPreprocessor 